334
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:26,250
[The Game: Towards Zero]

335
00:33:26,250 --> 00:33:29,720
Jo Pil Doo wasn't the 
one who killed our Mi Jin?

336
00:33:29,720 --> 00:33:34,690
I'll make sure to find him. 
I'll kill the bastard who killed Mi Jin.

337
00:33:34,690 --> 00:33:37,180
You think I'm a monster, don't you?

338
00:33:37,180 --> 00:33:40,170
Will you still think so after 
losing someone precious?

339
00:33:40,170 --> 00:33:41,670
I'll lock him up immediately.

340
00:33:41,670 --> 00:33:45,030
Is this what you meant by, 
"locking up immediately?"

341
00:33:45,030 --> 00:33:49,540
You should've apologized 20 years ago!

342
00:33:49,540 --> 00:33:51,840
Don't you think?

343
00:33:54,860 --> 00:33:56,680
Who are you?
